  "3249600": {
    "name": "徨恍 Aware",
    "steam_appid": 3249600,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras/bf50d049ce849af5990a96efba1e56cc.avif?t=1770478773\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras_big/bf50d049ce849af5990a96efba1e56cc.avif?t=1770478773 width=800 height=1241 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演一名侦探，回到七十余载前的冬日北平，感受冷冽、虚无、探寻、追逐、戏剧与枪响。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras/bfabe04879cf5bd2bc04e1cd49bbaa31.avif?t=1770478773\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras_big/bfabe04879cf5bd2bc04e1cd49bbaa31.avif?t=1770478773 width=800 height=112 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1949年初，冬。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >天津战役即将打响，北平的傅作义部正考虑和谈。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >秋，作为保密局南京总部的一员，被密派前往北平，同上级路一起破坏和平谈判。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大学生雪因秋伪装的侦探身份而找上门来，请求秋寻找自己失踪的恋人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，一开始，秋就知道，这是无法完成的任务，不论是寻找那位“恋人”，还是破坏谈判……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >枪声回荡于北平的雪夜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >零落、寂寥的炮火声下，些许虚无与狂气的故事就此拉开序幕——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras/bb108789b1dccf74c439605324331b49.avif?t=1770478773\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras_big/bb108789b1dccf74c439605324331b49.avif?t=1770478773 width=800 height=112 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事背景为民国末年，时间为1948年12月至1949年1月。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事地点主要在北平。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当时，国民党溃败，解放军兵临北平城外。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和平前夕，危机四伏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras/a1dfcb2733d9af550978c7b7028d66c5.avif?t=1770478773\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras_big/a1dfcb2733d9af550978c7b7028d66c5.avif?t=1770478773 width=800 height=112 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras/030c83b7d6782b9c0f5d46ab1c5a7218.avif?t=1770478773\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras_big/030c83b7d6782b9c0f5d46ab1c5a7218.avif?t=1770478773 width=800 height=396 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >秋是玩家所扮演的角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身为南京保密局总部行动处特务，曾在抗战时期立下战功。现以“侦探”身份活动于北平，听命于路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras/20f101d4ee332a3494ab7ae0a7b744b6.avif?t=1770478773\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras_big/20f101d4ee332a3494ab7ae0a7b744b6.avif?t=1770478773 width=800 height=396 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大学生，学校剧社的演员，中央通讯社北平分社主编的女儿。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras/068f8643bfc47aa01104ff4ebb704ce6.avif?t=1770478773\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras_big/068f8643bfc47aa01104ff4ebb704ce6.avif?t=1770478773 width=800 height=396 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >南京保密局总部情报处特务，带领秋等人受命于北平从事破坏活动。由年轻时“三民主义”的信仰者渐渐转变。现以“中央通讯社北平分社副主编”的身份活动于北平。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras/6396463791cbbafa945534635f3e97f5.avif?t=1770478773\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras_big/6396463791cbbafa945534635f3e97f5.avif?t=1770478773 width=800 height=396 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大学生，学校剧社的演员、编剧，雪的学姐。北平前市长的外甥女。即将于自创剧目《落红》饰演女主角。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras/cdef0d790db75e01fe0d25e829058886.avif?t=1770478773\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras_big/cdef0d790db75e01fe0d25e829058886.avif?t=1770478773 width=800 height=396 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大学生，学校剧社的演员，进步青年。负责组织学生运动，同市内民主进步人士联络，并向解放军传递情报。失踪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras/9e692e6211fe7fb97e1298e3b5a41d18.avif?t=1770478773\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras_big/9e692e6211fe7fb97e1298e3b5a41d18.avif?t=1770478773 width=800 height=112 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作剧本由乌镇戏剧节演出剧目编剧团队操刀，大胆的台词打破传统主旋律“喊口号”式的枯燥无味。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5小时体验，多结局分支，细微选择或可导向完全不同的故事路线。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras/2d9d7c1802519328b13d87e91325d11e.avif?t=1770478773\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras/5bec5aeec0cdd1cdab7fbf229b1cc3b2.avif?t=1770478773\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras/a51eea7efadd9c13958b411e7ebf7bc0.avif?t=1770478773\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras/66d11a1d330a7e402e338aedd4d52f1b.avif?t=1770478773\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras/2a63220d1546760d19cd3f6923f6f350.avif?t=1770478773\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras_big/2a63220d1546760d19cd3f6923f6f350.avif?t=1770478773 width=800 height=112 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >国产视觉小说顶级视效，UE5场景渲染多镜头演绎。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >考究民国服装、建筑等元素，兼顾历史真实与美感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras/41b1b364e73305fe2186db18eb5c1ffd.avif?t=1770478773\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras_big/41b1b364e73305fe2186db18eb5c1ffd.avif?t=1770478773 width=800 height=112 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >屡获大奖的配乐师负责配乐，打造影视级听觉体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >中央戏剧学院科班出身演员进行配音，带来话剧级演出效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras/4969f4cacdb15a6e8f74ae3d4d79c3d9.avif?t=1770478773\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249600/extras_big/4969f4cacdb15a6e8f74ae3d4d79c3d9.avif?t=1770478773 width=800 height=112 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制作组：《徨恍Aware》制作组</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制作人/剧本原案及定稿：Rlz</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >剧本初稿：小波</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >概念设计：自言自语Bot、粉红恶魔鲨了你</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色设计：牧和</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >场景设计：海狗</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CG原画：牧和</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >程序：刘贝</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UI/美宣：牧和</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >配乐：樊天谷</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
